claim.claim-text:
25. The panel crimping machine of claim 21, wherein said drive trains comprises: 
(a) a first shaft extending through said male crimping roller; 
(b) a second shaft extending through said female crimping roller; 
(c) a first gear mounted on said first shaft; 
(d) a second gear mounted on said second shaft, said second gear engaging said first gear; 
(e) an idler sprocket engaging said second sprocket; and 
(f) a motor connected to and driving said idler gear, which in turn rotates said first and second gears, thereby rotating said male and female crimping rollers.
